SCOREJOBS runs server-side Mercury-style proximity scoring of every open job listing against a single candidate's profile. Params: PARAM.salary_target, PARAM.exp_target, PARAM.remote_pref. Weights: salary_max proximity 3, experience proximity 2, remote match 2 (max score 7, normalized to 0-1). Output pipe-delimited with score first, highest-to-lowest. Used by the candidate's "Top Matches" view. This demonstrates server-side scoring — frontend used to compute Mercury client-side which failed the showcase mission.
